column5: Well the fishing has finally starting to get Hot the Tuna have been on Fire and now the sailfish are showing up in big number here are a few Warm Weather Fishing Porn Pics from Pacific Coast Costa Rica

Those pics are XXXX rated Steve. I hope you have a great season. I got to Florida for the holidays so I have some vitamin C built up and I'm not to jealous of you 2 this year.There isn't any snow here, haven't used the shovel. I hope they have cleared the mouth of the river. There is pack ice to Caledonia not moving. I was in town today and it was pouring hard. The storm sewers were backing up in front of Giant Tiger and the $ store.
Much prefer the Salt Water life ...and not looking at the soggy ice winter after winter ...lakes wide open should go out this year ...
I didn't make it to Maitland to check. Good to hear that it's clear. We do have about a par 4 of ice on the point. Here today gone tomorrow. Again good fishing and enjoy.
